### Global Variables
@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1. 출석 코드 생성 (교사) - *수업이 있어야 함*
POST {{host}}/api/v1/attendance/codes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token_teacher}}

{
  "courseId": {{course_id}},
  "validMinutes": 10
}

> {%
  client.global.set("attendance_code", response.body.data.code);
%}

### 2. 출석 체크 (학생)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/attendance/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token_student}}

{
  "courseId": {{course_id}},
  "authCode": "{{attendance_code}}"
}

### 3. 출석 정정 요청 (학생 -> 교사)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/attendance/corrections
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token_student}}

{
  "enrollmentId": 1, 
  "attendanceDate": "2026-04-01",
  "reason": "병원 진료"
}

### 4. 출석 정정 승인 (교사)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/attendance/corrections/1/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token_teacher}}


